{"tid":1562243,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（Sir this way!)美國參議院通過《新疆人權政策法案》","createTime":"2019-09-12T02:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T03:21:08.000Z","uid":125168,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"965bbaaa1479e1b830c65368f7b37f8833828348","tid":1562243,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:44:59.000Z","msg":"美國參議院通過《新疆人權政策法案》。<br />\n<br />\n法案要求美國多個政府部門，就中國打壓新疆維吾爾族向國會提交報告，其中國務院須每年匯報當地鎮壓情況，包括再教育營關押人數、是否存在強逼勞動、政府監控規模等。國務卿亦應評估能否按現行機制，例如引用《馬格尼茨基法案》，制裁包括新疆書記在內涉及侵犯人權的中國官員。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法案由共和黨參議員魯比奧提出，獲跨黨派支持，眾議院正排期審議，如果順利通過，經總統特朗普簽署後將正式成為法律。"},{"pid":"f6efa7f9a0aecb50a7e2f503151d3fc113923c8c","tid":1562243,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:45:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"e8ae71522d9c00f34ad023a4707add365e69214e","tid":1562243,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:46:10.000Z","msg":"香港人權與民主法案還會遠嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3f39bdf232c3ebfbdf3e70681f693104848dbd","tid":1562243,"uid":46408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:46:55.000Z","msg":"習近平有回血劍<br />\n美國都有<br />\n炒撚晒你係外國既貪官資產<br />\n再拎黎打返你條仆街"},{"pid":"aa662267c70e5e1d55d1895e18ef7bfc2592ea32","tid":1562243,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:47:03.000Z","msg":"我地要做嘢令香港法案加辣"},{"pid":"45fd6ae8e3af67d5c9ad80d1d692fc369f1d9779","tid":1562243,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:47:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2775a62b65f2ac10dd446b2542bcae9f516b8e99","tid":1562243,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:49:29.000Z","msg":"我是護旗手🇺🇸"},{"pid":"d784dc801f3b6d4ee61d5da5cefeb0ed6325ef90","tid":1562243,"uid":35648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:49:38.000Z","msg":"Title:通過<br />\n<br />\n內文：<br />\n<blockquote>法案由共和黨參議員魯比奧提出，獲跨黨派支持，眾議院正排期審議，<span style=\"color: red;\">如果順利通過</span>，經總統特朗普簽署後將正式成為法律。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be8faa7c70053813405090318cb125f4f0798286","tid":1562243,"uid":261332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:50:25.000Z","msg":"篇野噏乜柒呀？<br />\ntitel又話『參議院』通過，內文又話『眾議院』排緊期。<br />\n然後又話『眾議院』如果通過後總統簽署就生效。<br />\n<br />\n多矛盾都算，連概念都錯。係參議院通過後先到總統簽署。唔係眾議院。"},{"pid":"02823710c936dcea9ece636e0d89bc2bfc2710f4","tid":1562243,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:51:45.000Z","msg":"source: cable news"},{"pid":"149762a855c07bfb82159f5a1d1a3ec883e1fdeb","tid":1562243,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be8faa7c70053813405090318cb125f4f0798286","tid":1562243,"uid":261332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T0